Structure. Body 1.3–1.9 times as long as wide. Antenna 8-segmented, 1.3–1.9 times as long as forewing pad. Marginal setae on forewing pad weakly capitate, short and medium long, mostly shorter than distance between bases of adjacent setae; setae on dorsum of wing pads weakly capitate. Circumanal ring small, weakly indented anteriorly (
Fig. 173
).

Measurements (in mm) and ratios (
23 immatures
). Body length 1.00–1.90, antenna length 0.66–0.92.
